Leading Ladies in Avengers: From Zero to Hero

Kate Bruncati, Lauren Cox, Emilia Field

4/29/2019

Scarlett Johansson (left) and Brie Larson (right)

1

Scarlett Johansson - Top 5 Rated Movies

SELECT t.title, t.production_year, mii2.info AS rating, r.role
FROM cast_info ci
JOIN title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN movie_info_idx mii2 ON mii2.movie_id = t.id
JOIN role_type r ON r.id = ci.role_id
WHERE ci.person_id = 3305349
AND t.kind_id = 1
AND mii2.info_type_id = 101
AND r.id = 2
GROUP BY title
ORDER BY rating desc
LIMIT 0,5
5 records
title production_year rating role
The Prestige 2006 8.5 actress
The Avengers 2012 8.1 actress
Her 2013 8.0 actress
Captain America: Civil War 2016 7.9 actress
Captain America: The Winter Soldier 2014 7.8 actress

Brie Larson - Top 5 Rated Movies

SELECT t.title, t.production_year, mii2.info AS rating, r.role
FROM cast_info ci
JOIN title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN movie_info_idx mii2 ON mii2.movie_id = t.id
JOIN role_type r ON r.id = ci.role_id
WHERE ci.person_id = 3410664 
AND t.kind_id = 1
AND mii2.info_type_id = 101
AND r.id = 2
ORDER BY rating desc
LIMIT 0, 5;
